# Video Calling Backend

This is the backend server for a video calling application.  
It handles meeting creation, signaling, and SFU-based media routing.

---

## Features
- Create & manage meeting rooms  
- Real-time signaling with Socket.IO  
- WebRTC SFU media routing (mediasoup-style architecture)  
- MongoDB for meeting persistence  
- Express REST API  
- CORS support for frontend integration  

---

## Tech Stack
- Node.js  
- Express  
- Socket.IO  
- MongoDB + Mongoose  
- Mediasoup-based SFU  
- Nodemon (development)

---

## Project Structure

videoCalling_backend/
├─ config/
│ ├─ db.js
│ └─ mediasoup.js
├─ controllers/
│ └─ meetingController.js
├─ models/
│ └─ Meeting.js
├─ routes/
│ └─ meetingRoutes.js
├─ sockets/
│ ├─ signaling.js
│ └─ sfuRoom.js
├─ app.js
└─ server.js
